essional manufacturer   ', 0, '2019-03-23 13:01:25', NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (16, 'Mirror_aluminum_substrate_COB_16', '2019-01-16 09:47:08', NULL, 208, 18, 0, '<p>\n    <img src=\"https://www.pcbonline.com/file/2019-01-27/2017120505541525.jpg\" alt=\"pcb  prototype\">\n</p>\n<h2>Mirror silver aluminum substrate</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p data-group=\"1-1\" class=\"src highlight\">Mirror silver aluminum substrate is the most suitable raw material for COB packaging.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p data-group=\"1-1\" class=\"src highlight\">\n            <img src=\"https://www.pcbonline.com/file/2019-01-27/3969979.jpg\" alt=\"pcb  online\">\n        </p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <h2 class=\"word\">\n            <span class=\"basic-word\">&nbsp;Aluminum Advantages</span>\n        </h2>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p data-group=\"1-1\" class=\"src highlight\">1. Good heat dissipation: the mirror silver-aluminum substrate adopts thermoelectric separation technology, and the thermal conductivity of ordinary aluminum substrate with insulation layer is 1W, 1.5w, and 2W.The thermal conductivity of mirror aluminum is 137W, which greatly improves the heat dissipation of the chip.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n            <span>\n                <img src=\"https://www.pcbonline.com/file/2019-01-27/73815124.jpg\" alt=\"PCB Quote\">\n                <br>\n            </span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n            <span>\n            </span>\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n            <span>2. High light efficiency: the reflectivity of the ordinary gold-immersed aluminum substrate is 80%, the reflectivity of cup hole aluminum substrate is 85%, the reflectivity of the silver-plated aluminum substrate is 95%, the reflectivity of mirror silver-aluminum substrate is 98%.Mirror silver aluminum substrate can make the chip light better excited out.</span>\n            <span>\n                <o:p>\n                </o:p>\n            </span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n            <span>\n                <img src=\"https://www.pcbonline.com/file/2019-01-27/573882637.jpg\" alt=\"PCB Manufacturer\">\n                <br>\n            </span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n            <span>\n            </span>\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n            <span>3. Easy operation: the structure of the mirror silver-aluminum substrate is similar to the integrated bracket used in our market, and the circuit is connected by a gold wire.</span>\n        </p>\n    </li>\n</ul>', 'PCB Technology', 1, 1, 2, 'admin', NULL, 'Mirror aluminum substrate COB | The best pcb manufacturer in china', 'pcb prototyping, cheap pcb, Low Cost PCB', 'PCBonline is the easy and quick solution for the online buying of printed circuits board with high quality through a very professional service', 0, '2019-03-27 21:16:13', NULL);
